{"tid":1562151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人話要係ifc搞快閃","createTime":"2019-09-12T02:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T05:45:42.000Z","uid":275401,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"eedf155b31b6b562d78b490de49e3722b9695bf7","tid":1562151,"uid":275401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:00:28.000Z","msg":"p牌仔第一次開po<br />\n朋友做支那公司 d支那人發起左個咁嘅活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地一堆支那公司有個大group 話搞d青年活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSorry係殘體字因為我照copy<br />\n<br />\n【9.12，1:00pm，IFC快闪】<br />\n各位好，把今天的活动流程简单整理一下，因为是临时组织的快闪，没有专业音箱设备，没有麦克风，所以现场只能凭来参加的小伙伴齐声高歌，让全港都听到我们的心声！<br />\n<br />\n1、请大家12:45到IFC中庭Greyhound附近集合，集合处会有小伙伴手撑国旗，尽量靠拢一些。<br />\n2、活动1:00pm准时开始，合唱两首：1、《国歌》，2、《歌唱祖国》，会有三位群友领唱，大家一起合唱。<br />\n3、唱完后领唱会喊口号，大家只要大声复述即可（分别普通话、广东话、英文）：我爱中国！我爱香港！We Love China！We Love Hong Kong！<br />\n4、解散。<br />\n<br />\n有几点需请各位注意：<br />\n1、没有dress code，服饰随意。<br />\n2、上午会有歌词图片发给大家，请保存。<br />\n3、活动结束后各自吃饭逛街，如遇不合理行为，直接走开或报警，不要有任何冲突。<br />\n<br />\n最后，请大家注意安全！我们IFC见~~~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3C0xHD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3C0xHD.png&h=a2e45298&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c42e948e9403db8cd3701f789d98bb16dfbcdcb8","tid":1562151,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:01:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9c016b286399f98b16a2e19ca6b59c65cf31997","tid":1562151,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:01:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"5d3920c9f176937de3eaa798e63e4ca8bb3ec77f","tid":1562151,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:01:57.000Z","msg":"歡迎呀<br />\n<br />\n對家做咩都柒過人<br />\n最驚佢唔出手"},{"pid":"062f5c42c8b456a73cfb340e22af378409337719","tid":1562151,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:02:20.000Z","msg":"留名等恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347771a2d5422a56c16a5151aa6c05c8dba6d363","tid":1562151,"uid":188311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:02:30.000Z","msg":"好彩未立國歌法ja<br />\n大陸唔撚比人周圍唱國歌嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6df662aac8802b8b84a36b0b565c12f002ae54","tid":1562151,"uid":304321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:03:06.000Z","msg":"唔該係中環返工既巴絲到時可唔可以影下相比我地睇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10ec01b51bcd4cf02463377c8b2ce56a4a923be","tid":1562151,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:03:15.000Z","msg":"free Hong kong,  free chinazi <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e99c17a2399da51746c70210149693f9a5680e3","tid":1562151,"uid":132287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl